ative defaults: tempo_deviation_pct=4, dynamic_range_db=9, arc_peak_position=0.6, breath_after_ms=250, restraint=0.0<br/>- tests verify defaults match research-calibrated KTH k=1 values and reject out-of-range inputs |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 31 | T-031 | Implement SectionEnvelope with breakpoint functions over tempo_base, density_target, dynamic_plane, brightness, tension_trajectory. | T1 | 3 | 3 | CCH-003 | T-001 | - `render/events.py` defines SectionEnvelope with breakpoint-function interpolation (linear default, optional spline)<br/>- envelope samples at arbitrary normalized position 0..1 within section<br/>- phrase-arc rules compose multiplicatively with section-envelope samples<br/>- tests verify interpolation, composition with phrase arcs, and parameter bounds |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 32 | T-032 | Define IntentTag enum (build/settle/question/answer/withhold/punctuate) and require every phrase to carry one. | T1 | 3 | 3 | CCH-004 | T-001 | - IntentTag enum exists in `render/events.py` with exactly six values<br/>- composition gate rejects phrases missing intent_tag on long pieces<br/>- micro pieces may use punctuate as the default<br/>- tests verify enum completeness and gate rejection path |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 33 | T-033 | Define Role enum (ostinato/melody/pad/perc/accent/silence) with grid_locked flag and role-filter policy used by all rules. | T1 | 6 | 3 | CCH-005 | T-001 | - Role enum exists with grid_locked boolean attribute (ostinato=True, perc=True, melody=False, pad=False, accent=False, silence=N/A)<br/>- every rule in the stack respects a shared `rule.applies_to(role)` filter so grid-locked voices skip R1–R8<br/>- tests verify grid-locked voices emerge from the render pass with timing_deviation_ms == 0 and no microtiming jitter |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 34 | T-034 | Implement seeded-RNG architecture with per-stage sub-seeds derived from a root seed along a seed_path tuple. | T1 | 5 | 3 | CCH-006 | T-001 | - `render/seed.py` exposes derive_seed(root_seed, path_tuple